rComments: Prof speaks very low and can be difficult to hear what she is saying. She does want her students to do well though and tries to simplify things for you to achieve good grades. Her multiple choice is challenging and is heavily based on textbook. SA are straight forward and easy if you pay attention to lecture. Overall not a bad prof and would retake

She mumbles quite a lot. Sometimes she talks really fast especially for the experiments, and she doesn't repeat what she says. The tests are somewhat difficult. The short answers are okay if you study her slides really well. But multiple choice is brutal if you don't study the textbook.
